HOW TO BLAST
So, you want to join the Styleblaster Network?

Camera setup instructions:
Styleblaster is designed to work with a high definition webcam.
We recommend Microsoft Lifecam Studio (http://www.amazon.com/Microsoft-LifeCam-Studio-1080p-Webcam/dp/B0042X8NT6). Logitech cameras are not recommended due to their short focus range.



Need the postToWeb Processing library to run the processing sketch.
Download here: http://libraries.seltar.org/postToWeb/

